Module org.phenopackets.phenopackettools.validator.jsonschema

module org.phenopackets.phenopackettools.validator.jsonschema
Defines a ValidationWorkflowRunner with base validation backed by a JSON schema.

The module provides JsonSchemaValidationWorkflowRunner an implementation of ValidationWorkflowRunner backed by a JSON schema validator.
